snippet.title: You Probably Shouldn't Jump From Job To Job. Paul Douglas Moomjean
snippet.description:
You probably shouldn't jump from job to job and Paul Douglas Moomjean is a perfect example of why. In this clip from his full Dry Bar Comedy special Paul breaks down the many jobs he's had across his career before ending up as a comedian. Whether you're someone who likes to hop from job to job, or someone who has been in the same job your entire life this clip form Paul Moomjean's full Dry Bar Comedy special is sure to keep you entertained from start to finish.

Watch Paul Moomjean's full special exclusively on Dry Bar Comedy +
https://www.drybarcomedy.com/paulmoomjean
